Sometimes it’s okay to slouch. Made of non-stretch, organic cotton denim for a vintage-inspired look, the Rigid Slouch Jean features a straight, slouchy fit that sits at the perfect spot: on your hips and just below your belly button. Plus, it has a longer, 27.5" inseam and a relaxed, straight leg, which gives it a comfortable, laid-back feel. Consider it the next evolution of boyfriend jeans.
